annotationA: Putative fatty acyl-CoA reductase CG5065; Catalyzes the reduction of C16 or C18 fatty acyl-CoA to fatty alcohols
annotationB: Alkyldihydroxyacetonephosphate synthase; Catalyzes the exchange of an acyl for a long-chain alkyl group and the formation of the ether bond in the biosynthesis of ether phospholipids; Belongs to the FAD-binding oxidoreductase/transferase type 4 family
